{"type":"text","timestamp":1775907571046,"sessionID":"ses_283add0daffeXnLlAzhiHku2PX","part":{"id":"prt_d7c5692b8001Exv3Jw0rwCziIa","messageID":"msg_d7c55f50a001zwPuDVEdwi1bic","sessionID":"ses_283add0daffeXnLlAzhiHku2PX","type":"text","text":"I've written the `proposal.md` file for **AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端**. The proposal includes:\n\n## Summary\n\n| Section | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| **Purpose** | HTTP low-level client layer foundation for AgentCube Python SDK |\n| **Scope** | HTTP session factory, authentication utilities, logging, exception hierarchy, control plane & data plane HTTP clients |\n| **Design** | Architecture diagrams, class structures, HTTP endpoint mappings for Workload Manager and Router APIs |\n| **Impact Analysis** | 10 affected components, dependencies (requests, PyJWT, cryptography), timeout/config behavior |\n| **Alternatives Considered** | 8 alternatives analyzed (httpx vs requests, Pydantic models, auto-generated clients, etc.) |\n| **Verification** | Code examples for testing each component |\n| **Success Criteria** | 18 specific completion criteria |\n\n### Key Design Decisions\n\n1. **requests library** — Chosen over httpx for familiarity and stability\n2. **Connection pooling** — Default 10 connections, 10 max pool size\n3. **Timeout defaults** — 5.0s connect, 120s read timeout\n4. **Separate client classes** — ControlPlaneClient, CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient, AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\n5. **Exception hierarchy** — AgentCubeError base with CommandExecutionError, SessionError, DataPlaneError\n6. **Service account auth** — Auto-read from `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token`","time":{"start":1775907571043,"end":1775907571043}}}
